conref="wskc_conref-l0wskc04.dita#conref-l0wskc04/cca"/>): PKA key management</searchtitle>
</titlealts>
<shortdesc>You can generate RSA and ECC keys using the <keyword
conref="wskc_conref-l0wskc04.dita#conref-l0wskc04/vbnmpkg"/> verb (<keyword
conref="wskc_conref-l0wskc04.dita#conref-l0wskc04/vbclpkg"/>), or a comparable product from another
vendor.</shortdesc>
